re-block:
Name of the MediaWiki log action 'block', but describes a value that includes both blocks and re-blocks.
{{Identical|Block}}
{{Identical|Reblock}}

re-blocks:
Label for number of times a user has been blocked or re-blocked. Try to keep this message brief.
{{Identical|Block}}
{{Identical|Reblock}}

re-protect:
Name of the MediaWiki log action 'protect', but describes a value that includes protections or re-protections.
{{Identical|Protect}}
{{Identical|Reprotect}}

tsv:
{{Optional}}
Link for TSV file. See https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tab-separated_values for information on what a TSV file is.
TSV is the name of a file format and should probably not be translated.
